school pack features interesting information on the Karen as well as ways for young people to think about poverty, disadvantage and how they can help. It can be used as a supplementary activity in school and will enrich young minds and open them up to knowledge about a forgotten and unknown people with a fascinating culture and history. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We encourage teachers to download this resource and get in touch with us! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can contact us on: info@karenhilltribes.org.uk <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The Karen Hilltribes Trust works to provide improve&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":13995,"parent":159,"menu_order":5,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_mi_skip_tracking":false},"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.12 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Schools Supporting KHT - Karen Hilltribes Trust<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/get-involved\/schools-supporting-kht\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Schools Supporting KHT - Karen Hilltribes Trust\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"The Karen Hilltribes Trust works to provide improve...\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/get-involved\/schools-supporting-kht\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Karen Hilltribes Trust\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:modified_time\" content=\"2023-07-10T13:04:15+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/POSTER.png\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"848\" \/>\n\t<me